# Ticket #2 – Password Reset

## Issue:
The user cannot remember their password

## Investigation:
Opened Active Directory and the client computer
Located the user account
Verified that the account is not disabled
Confirmed that the account is not locked

## Root Cause:
The user was on leave and has forgotten their password

## Resolution:
In Active Directory, I located the user and reset their password
Created a temporary password that the user will use to log in to change their password
Had the user log in and reset their password

## Verification:
User logged in to the workstation successfully

## Lessons Learned
In Active Directory, checking the box that the user must change their password on their next login is not enough to reset their password
Help Desk can manually change the password if necessary
